description: Petco Adjustable Mesh Harness for Big and Tall Dogs in Black & GrayOur Petco Adjustable Mesh Harness for Big and Tall Dogs is a super-stylish ultra-comfortable harness. The gunmetal finish metal hardware adds flair while the bold colors really show off your Big and Tall dog's sense of style. Lightly padded material with breathable mesh provides the utmost comfort. Designed with easy slide-and-lock tabs (much like how a ski boot works) at the neck and adjustable slides in the chest area, this harness will have a snug and custom fit for your Big and Tall dog. This harness also has a longer back piece to allow for a better fit on more breeds. Harness also includes a heavy-duty plastic snap lock buckle for extra security. The nylon strap has two metal D-rings for attaching a leash. The second D-ring is positioned to allow you to put a coat or safety vest on your pooch without having to remove the harness. This harness even includes an extra tab for clipping on an ID Tag or charm. In addition to being comfy, stylish and featuring added safety measures for your furry friend, this body harness alleviates pulling and strain and helps to distribute your Big and Tall dog's body weight evenly. The V-shape neckline is designed so that when the dog pulls on its lead, the harness pulls at the chest and not the neck. This provides a better walking experience for both you and your pet.
